sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant RP as ReferencePrecalculator
    participant DIS as Dispatcher
    participant AD as Output Adapter
    participant BR as Bridge
    participant RS as Read-Side / Receiver Boundary

    RP-->>DIS: TDispatchAccessRef
    DIS->>DIS: validate push dispatch profile
    DIS->>AD: push dispatch attempt
    AD->>BR: bridge-facing send/action
    BR->>RS: bridge/read-side transfer
    AD-->>DIS: push attempt result
    DIS->>DIS: report push result / update exposure state

    Note over DIS,RS: Push is optional profile-bound behavior, not CME core identity.
